    {
      "id": "PopularPost353443",
      "post_content": "It's one of the [few](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=29922) [useful](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=4877) [non](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=5588)-\"[enchant](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=6046) [creature](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=238136)\" [enchantments](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=1624) for {W} [or](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=107699) [less](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=204993).  \n  \nThese enchantments go a long way to making a [Serra's Sanctum](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Serra's Sanctum) deck actually playable. Not as broken as his [cousin](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=8883), but playable. Unfortunately, as I just pointed out, this is outclassed by other cheap white enchantments. I would, however, consider running one or two of this in a {U}/{W} manland deck, with Teferi's Response being the playset of counters.",
      "posted_by": "MacBizzle",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost353443\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_post\">It's one of the <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardid=\"29922\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=29922\">few</a> <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardid=\"4877\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=4877\">useful</a> <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardid=\"5588\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=5588\">non</a>-\"<a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardid=\"6046\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=6046\">enchant</a> <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardid=\"238136\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=238136\">creature</a>\" <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardid=\"1624\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=1624\">enchantments</a> for {W} <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardid=\"107699\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=107699\">or</a> <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardid=\"204993\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=204993\">less</a>.<br/><br/>These enchantments go a long way to making a <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Serra's Sanctum\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Serra's Sanctum\">Serra's Sanctum</a> deck actually playable. Not as broken as his <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardid=\"8883\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=8883\">cousin</a>, but playable. Unfortunately, as I just pointed out, this is outclassed by other cheap white enchantments. I would, however, consider running one or two of this in a {U}/{W} manland deck, with Teferi's Response being the playset of counters.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '353443'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy46803\">MacBizzle</span>\r\n                                (12/4/2013 12:42:36 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>"
