    {
      "id": "PopularPost373285",
      "post_content": "@deworde2510: Current oracle wording is fine. You can target any spell, and if, at the time of the Equinox ability's resolution, that target spell resolving would cause a land to be destroyed, it is countered. The infinite loop described would not happen, because the evaluation of whether the spell should be countered only happens once.  \n  \nAs for the card itself, it belongs in the sideboard if your metagame somehow calls for it. Otherwise, to the museum!",
      "posted_by": "Mainstay",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost373285\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">@deworde2510: Current oracle wording is fine.  You can target any spell, and if, at the time of the Equinox ability's resolution, that target spell resolving would cause a land to be destroyed, it is countered.   The infinite loop described would not happen, because the evaluation of whether the spell should be countered only happens once.<br/><br/>As for the card itself, it belongs in the sideboard if your metagame somehow calls for it.  Otherwise, to the museum!</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '373285'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy76954\">Mainstay</span>\r\n                                (4/26/2014 12:55:30 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../